unicate and play with the ghosts. Lu Bi went into labor, and the four ghosts competed to be reincarnated. Once, Lu Bi was saved by Zhuang Wei Qiang, who had a crush on her. Xiao also fell in love with Lu Bi, and they began a romance. Eventually, the three families faced eviction but became close friends after going through ups and downs together. The three families helped the ghosts reincarnate, and they tearfully said goodbye at a banquet.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"227075","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2025-11-18T15:20:58.000Z","cast":["Lưu Đan","Lau Kwok-Shing","Lung Tin-Sang","Tsang Choh-Lam","Lau Nga-Lai","Tăng Giang","Regina Tsang Hing-Yu","Cheung Ying-Tsoi","Louie Castro","Chan On-ying","Yip Ha-Lei","Kwong Joh-Fai","Michelle Sima"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Lưu Đan","name_vi":"Lưu Đan","name_original":"Danny Lau Dan","tmdb_id":1133980,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gEmCCnMg9GvskUPSuGQA3ae8irk.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1133980"},{"name":"Lau Kwok-Shing","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lau Kwok-Shing","tmdb_id":228586,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4fPzOjsgKNBoLkrpEP6UJ8NZ7Gk.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/228586"},{"name":"Lung Tin-Sang","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lung Tin-Sang","tmdb_id":955784,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hhypKuhDqqeEW9RpVUyCQ2YmSJN.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/955784"},{"name":"Tsang Choh-Lam","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Tsang Choh-Lam","tmdb_id":1180159,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ggVuG1PWbj2BioYODBocT90C4Pg.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1180159"},{"name":"Lau Nga-Lai","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lau Nga-Lai","tmdb_id":1359902,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1BaWJZ336qChlhDst3JBE4oX8n8.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1359902"},{"name":"Tăng Giang","name_vi":"Tăng Giang","name_original":"Kenneth Tsang","tmdb_id":10885,"p